<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>URL Shortener Home</title>
    <style>
      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f0f2f5;
        color: #333;
        padding: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        margin-top: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        color: #555;
      }

      .btn-container {
        margin: 2rem 0;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 1rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .btn {
        padding: 12px 24px;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.2);
      }

      .btn:hover {
        background-color: #0056b3;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 14px rgba(0, 86, 179, 0.3);
      }

      .features {
        margin-top: 3rem;
        text-align: left;
        max-width: 720px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        background: #fff;
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      }

      .features h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: #222;
      }

      .features ul {
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        color: #444;
        line-height: 1.8;
      }

      .features li {
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('./partials/navbar') %>

    <h1>Welcome to the URL Shortener</h1>
    <p>Create, share, and manage your short links easily.</p>

    <div class="btn-container">
      <a class="btn" href="/api/url">Generate Short URL</a>
      <a class="btn" href="/api/url/analytics">View All URL Details</a>
    </div>

    <div class="features">
      <h2>Features:</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>🔗 Generate short links from long URLs.</li>
        <li>📊 Track total click analytics for each URL.</li>
        <li>🕒 View timestamp history of all visits.</li>
        <li>🧾 Simple and clean user interface using EJS templates.</li>
        <li>🗑️ Option to delete old or unwanted short URLs.</li>
        <li>📁 MongoDB-backed data storage with Mongoose.</li>
        <li>🚀 Fast response using Express.js server.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
